flowchart TD
    Start([WebServerFactory 装配]) --> Cond{classpath 中<br/>存在哪个容器?}

    Cond -->|"org.apache.catalina.*<br/>org.apache.catalina.startup.Tomcat"| Tomcat[TomcatServletWebServerFactory]
    Cond -->|"org.eclipse.jetty.*"| Jetty[JettyServletWebServerFactory]
    Cond -->|"io.undertow.*"| Undertow[UndertowServletWebServerFactory]
    Cond -->|"都不存在"| None[报错:<br/>缺少嵌入式容器依赖]

    Tomcat --> Use[默认装配 Tomcat]
    Jetty --> Ex1[需排除 Tomcat 依赖]
    Undertow --> Ex2[需排除 Tomcat 依赖]

    Use --> Common[通过 @ConditionalOnMissingBean<br/>允许用户自定义覆盖]
    Ex1 --> Common
    Ex2 --> Common
    None --> End([应用启动失败])
    Common --> End2([createWebServer 使用工厂])

    classDef condNode fill:#fff3e0,stroke:#ef6c00,stroke-width:2px
    classDef factoryNode fill:#e3f2fd,stroke:#1565c0
    classDef failNode fill:#ffebee,stroke:#c62828
    class Cond condNode
    class Tomcat,Jetty,Undertow,Common factoryNode
    class None,End failNode
